== Creating repos

* git hub repo-init, repo-new
+* git hub repo-init mycoolstuff:
+* Creates directory
+* Creates repo on github
+* Clones repo
+* media/repo-init.ogv

----
== Handling Pull Requests

* git hub pr-list, pr-diff, pr-fetch
+* git hub pr-list: List pull requests for current repo
+* git hub pr-diff num: Show diff for pull request
+* git hub pr-fetch num: Fetch the pull request into a local branch
+* media/pr-fetch.ogv
